("010", "Causes the target to flinch. Inflicts double damage and (Gen 6) has perfect accuracy if the target is Minimized.\nGen 6+: Dragon Rush has effects against Minimized targets. Prior to Gen 6, it just causes the target to flinch."),
("011", "Causes the target to flinch. Fails if the user is not asleep."),
("012", "Causes the target to flinch. Fails if it isn't the user's first round in the battle."),
