("046", "Decreases the target's Special Defense by 1 stage."),
("047", "Decreases the target's accuracy by 1 stage."),
("048", "Decreases the target's evasiveness by 1 stage.\nGen 6+: Decreases the target's evasiveness by 2 stages instead."),
("049", "Decreases the target's evasiveness by 1 stage. Ends the effects of Aurora Veil, Light Screen, Mist, Reflect, Safeguard, Spikes, Stealth Rock, Sticky Web and Toxic Spikes on the target's side (even if the evasiveness wasn't changed).\nGen 6+: The effects are ended on both sides of the field."),
("04A", "Decreases the target's Attack and Defense by 1 stage each."),
("04B", "Decreases the target's Attack by 2 stages."),
("04C", "Decreases the target's Defense by 2 stages."),
("04D", "Decreases the target's Speed by 2 stages.\nGen 6+: String Shot decreases the target's Speed by 2 stages. Prior to Gen 6, it lowers the target's Speed by 1 stage instead."),
